{"_id":"DxyovIcuVx8vImev","name":"James the Swordsman - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"James the Swordsman - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","notes":"James the Swordsman - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"u0QGAtviN9MWav8A","name":"James the Swordsman - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"James the Swordsman - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","notes":"James the Swordsman - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9teTnZ4LEZPyXY1W","name":"James the Swordsman - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"James the Swordsman - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","notes":"James the Swordsman - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"JbQuFndVRU7zoekw","name":"James the Swordsman - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"James the Swordsman - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","notes":"James the Swordsman - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"nq1JjIYuPMCnBdAJ","name":"Garou the Old Wolf - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou the Old Wolf - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","notes":"Garou the Old Wolf - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"3cJZIHkJW6wMHWoJ","name":"Garou the Old Wolf - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou the Old Wolf - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","notes":"Garou the Old Wolf - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"sKu6CWN2ZICx5440","name":"Garou the Old Wolf - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou the Old Wolf - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","notes":"Garou the Old Wolf - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"yvmcXk4rfbfCPZGz","name":"Garou the Old Wolf - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou the Old Wolf - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","notes":"Garou the Old Wolf - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"g0nGqWwbs8G72LHr","name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","notes":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241668,"modifiedTime":1783973241668,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MCfW0kzydy7dRFoJ","name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","notes":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"XTLASIs6GFdhm0j1","name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","notes":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"xzkjO3iUrZVSoKVO","name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","notes":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"hnJNRO13PcKdsK8F","name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","notes":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"40qCa3tJ3I0Nqmdh","name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","notes":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Brg7ZmWkhvhUXj47","name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","notes":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"l7EOT8Km7TjJT58E","name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","notes":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"eLW1z4GaxBbPN83M","name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","notes":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qw2VtevWd4VleaQy","name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","notes":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"wmUWLqkVUxmxJXzI","name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","notes":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"P9pc6zJfVLMmskLe","name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","notes":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"tKXmZtLZUwR9163e","name":"Babai the Judge - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai the Judge - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","notes":"Babai the Judge - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"0ugEoDECFqJVUFId","name":"Babai the Judge - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai the Judge - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","notes":"Babai the Judge - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ifK1dNtByrth7cRr","name":"Babai the Judge - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai the Judge - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","notes":"Babai the Judge - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"YOqFUSh6RUgvVSW1","name":"Babai the Judge - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai the Judge - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","notes":"Babai the Judge - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"4b3Ns9TbqJuXV7Wn","name":"The Woman from the Woods - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","notes":"The Woman from the Woods - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vi2wHm4tX5bKhoMR","name":"The Woman from the Woods - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","notes":"The Woman from the Woods - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241669,"modifiedTime":1783973241669,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"XxDgXiEUpR0RPowr","name":"The Woman from the Woods - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","notes":"The Woman from the Woods - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"mMOGA6ZuoJ2gbyyH","name":"The Woman from the Woods - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","notes":"The Woman from the Woods - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"UGJVC9ozcAvtNl47","name":"TheImmortal - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"TheImmortal - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","notes":"TheImmortal - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"YZxpZVAUgLSjMdZ9","name":"TheImmortal - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"TheImmortal - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","notes":"TheImmortal - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"bqjZ5ZB8VuxF7QZU","name":"TheImmortal - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"TheImmortal - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","notes":"TheImmortal - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"LlDkDGVWD8j600VP","name":"TheImmortal - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"TheImmortal - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","notes":"TheImmortal - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pSU4eqh3Q1jMwu2p","name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","notes":"Marina the Sea Explorer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qvTZDehKtLasIb4v","name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","notes":"Marina the Sea Explorer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"iVdWDYfo17HF8ezh","name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","notes":"Marina the Sea Explorer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"0rGImLvVa3giBzYM","name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","notes":"Marina the Sea Explorer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"EWJjpzYFK67aHVvA","name":"Niklaus von Krampus - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","notes":"Niklaus von Krampus - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"DBHAYdL8whn4xCrD","name":"Niklaus von Krampus - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","notes":"Niklaus von Krampus - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SbloEqm3p8AXsGc2","name":"Niklaus von Krampus - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","notes":"Niklaus von Krampus - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"67HvGC9eUqykIoEQ","name":"Niklaus von Krampus - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","notes":"Niklaus von Krampus - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241670,"modifiedTime":1783973241670,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"5Riis6zjy4EmOUdp","name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","notes":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"P0YfCml8YQr6JAJ2","name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","notes":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"CjyvPWgT8INHqdRw","name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","notes":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"zDIUVZM6Q2BwsnAl","name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","notes":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"f7vpQCAMUjTwzdPI","name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","notes":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9EQPheHLJ7p4rZSn","name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","notes":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"rwp4uAJ4PLZlGPDV","name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","notes":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"A8XBLfBt4GwT7mNV","name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","notes":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Iw0aDvYVjWNrpz9x","name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","notes":"Verdoux Bluebeard - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"4RyJjWDB9Ibdzwdt","name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","notes":"Verdoux Bluebeard - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"dHL53h9w2I1BGJ0j","name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","notes":"Verdoux Bluebeard - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"moQ4s8gvQVG2gDNq","name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","notes":"Verdoux Bluebeard - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"xH96Z8riqMYrZvqv","name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","notes":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"RcqZ1UxXGxUR95AJ","name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","notes":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vgkwwBMcVXO0Jawc","name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","notes":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"7DnuY11SIbNlXwWH","name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","notes":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241671,"modifiedTime":1783973241671,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SkRYeWiMp6RpVBms","name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","notes":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"6cvefbotRCPGLlnu","name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","notes":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"b2Fp5GyoBKfzi57m","name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","notes":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"DckmOYTt7DKEP2ZM","name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Descriptor 4","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Descriptor 4"}}}},"system":{"description":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","notes":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"nbOEQHAo3PcBd8P4","name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","notes":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"wbw4ym26Rk5bwyCc","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma when you use this Gift to blow a kiss to the target, \nthus avoiding physical contact.","notes":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma when you use this Gift to blow a kiss to the target, thus avoiding physical contact.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"NhPxNhPzvbVdKCey","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a novice a powerful sorceress with limited power total control \nover cold and snow. My magic can come with dangerous, unintended \nconsequences cause small unwanted effects.","notes":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am a novice a powerful sorceress with limited power total control over cold and snow. My magic can come with dangerous, unintended consequences cause small unwanted effects.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"rmnkmFJ83LCIYqny","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding dominating people. I have a unique \nability to comprehend their desires. I tend to distrust even close allies \ntrust those I don’t know.","notes":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am good at understanding dominating people. I have a unique ability to comprehend their desires. I tend to distrust even close allies trust those I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"gdDrCJ3p0WpHRlIX","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"Cold and frost have no effect on me are extensions of my soul and I feel \na great affinity for winter. My heart of pure ice delights is easily touched \nwhen I see others suffer.","notes":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cold and frost have no effect on me are extensions of my soul and I feel a great affinity for winter. My heart of pure ice delights is easily touched when I see others suffer.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"dlvvkuhVv3CEY3xU","name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have an encyclopedic memory and there is no law that I don’t \nknow. I hate to break the rules.","notes":"Tremoteus Rumpel - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have an encyclopedic memory and there is no law that I don’t know. I hate to break the rules.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"GPmcGrnI8X2Kc68w","name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"My reputation precedes me, and my word is held in the highest \nregard by anyone with an ounce of honesty. I detest criminals and \nthose who act to harm the innocent. Big or small, a crime is still \na crime.","notes":"Tremoteus Rumpel - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"My reputation precedes me, and my word is held in the highest regard by anyone with an ounce of honesty. I detest criminals and those who act to harm the innocent. Big or small, a crime is still a crime.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZI0af3gwZJfFfWt4","name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a keen disputant and have an uncanny ability to detect \ndeception. I need hard evidence before I’ll accuse someone of \ndishonesty.","notes":"Tremoteus Rumpel - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a keen disputant and have an uncanny ability to detect deception. I need hard evidence before I’ll accuse someone of dishonesty.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"eZW2wXXDFAMvC8M7","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying \nto persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you \nsuffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example \nfor those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your \nchoice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they \nmust use to try to help you or get you to safety.","notes":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying to persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you suffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example for those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your choice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they must use to try to help you or get you to safety.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"kszzLioMYPAPJOgr","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a young prince, well-versed in the etiquette of the court. I \nam a diligent student, my favorite subjects being history and \npoetry. I am not ashamed of my strange appearance and I hate to \nhide from others.","notes":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a young prince, well-versed in the etiquette of the court. I am a diligent student, my favorite subjects being history and poetry. I am not ashamed of my strange appearance and I hate to hide from others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"zEBFbsiNAuf38m08","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I use these qualities to uphold the good name of my family. I will \nnot allow anyone to violate the ideals of justice and courage with \nwhich I was raised.","notes":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I use these qualities to uphold the good name of my family. I will not allow anyone to violate the ideals of justice and courage with which I was raised.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"TNtZxPJIG9BfHbQL","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have strange powers, and my body is stronger and more resilient \nthan an ordinary child’s. While I’m not ashamed of my \nappearance, these uncanny abilities mark me as different, and I \ntry not to attract attention when I use my power.","notes":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I have strange powers, and my body is stronger and more resilient than an ordinary child’s. While I’m not ashamed of my appearance, these uncanny abilities mark me as different, and I try not to attract attention when I use my power.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"JFoPlFuPs0OomS9W","name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a rebel who is used to living on the streets. I know my way \naround the slums and how to deal with the lowlifes. Rules are \nmade to be broken.","notes":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a rebel who is used to living on the streets. I know my way around the slums and how to deal with the lowlifes. Rules are made to be broken.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"xfOjTBCir5bwBK6f","name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I fear nothing and throw myself into any situation. The \nadrenaline of risk drives me to succeed. I get bored easily in \nsituations where there is no danger.","notes":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I fear nothing and throw myself into any situation. The adrenaline of risk drives me to succeed. I get bored easily in situations where there is no danger.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"5Bma0Q2Wo440GF8X","name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"The Cauldron Fae is always with me, in the form of a small \nfloating light. Her magic is still powerful, and I often summon \nher to wreak havoc or play tricks on humans.","notes":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"The Cauldron Fae is always with me, in the form of a small floating light. Her magic is still powerful, and I often summon her to wreak havoc or play tricks on humans.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241672,"modifiedTime":1783973241672,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"h7M6AFhIVridK76b","name":"Loki the Deceiver - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Loki the Deceiver - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I can disguise myself to assume any identity. I can easily imitate \nmen, women, and even fantastical creatures. I have great respect \nfor a successful deception and hate to expose it, even if it would \nbenefit me.","notes":"Loki the Deceiver - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I can disguise myself to assume any identity. I can easily imitate men, women, and even fantastical creatures. I have great respect for a successful deception and hate to expose it, even if it would benefit me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"1k7eCbYIDNEhhBSP","name":"Loki the Deceiver - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Loki the Deceiver - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat, I tell stories, perform magic tricks, and put \nmy audience in a good mood. I enjoy chaos and adding confusion \nto situations is a way for me to bring balance to the world.","notes":"Loki the Deceiver - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat, I tell stories, perform magic tricks, and put my audience in a good mood. I enjoy chaos and adding confusion to situations is a way for me to bring balance to the world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"K9wILSNPYWiSGHLf","name":"Loki the Deceiver - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Loki the Deceiver - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a master at distorting and unraveling deception. Verbal \nand body language hold no secrets for me. I don’t like to get my \nhands dirty and would rather have someone else do it for me.","notes":"Loki the Deceiver - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a master at distorting and unraveling deception. Verbal and body language hold no secrets for me. I don’t like to get my hands dirty and would rather have someone else do it for me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZEwjL8uvWNkPouT0","name":"The Silent Mother - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Silent Mother - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I know my way around high society and have amassed great \nwealth through countless marriages. I am known in the \nunderworld for my exploits. I hate being accused of being a \ncriminal.","notes":"The Silent Mother - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I know my way around high society and have amassed great wealth through countless marriages. I am known in the underworld for my exploits. I hate being accused of being a criminal.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PBfdKkFNLakeBiNs","name":"The Silent Mother - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Silent Mother - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am able to understand the potential of young women and know \nhow to guide their steps to develop their true potential. I consider \neach of my protégés a true daughter and would give my life to \nsave them.","notes":"The Silent Mother - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am able to understand the potential of young women and know how to guide their steps to develop their true potential. I consider each of my protégés a true daughter and would give my life to save them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MpRVO9jv2bST1Umg","name":"The Silent Mother - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Silent Mother - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"Although I appear helpless, I am a capable spy who knows how to \ndefend herself in dangerous situations. I never miss an opportunity \nto accumulate wealth and resources.","notes":"The Silent Mother - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Although I appear helpless, I am a capable spy who knows how to defend herself in dangerous situations. I never miss an opportunity to accumulate wealth and resources.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"BxXLtQ6ZJNcBl5IC","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can mentally communicate for the rest of the Scene.","notes":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Y ou can mentally communicate for the rest of the Scene.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fMWfzUzeF7bM1UUi","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am an exorcist monk. My body is tempered by a lifetime of asceticism \nand fighting evil spirits. I do not tolerate blasphemy and those who use \nknowledge for personal gain.","notes":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I am an exorcist monk. My body is tempered by a lifetime of asceticism and fighting evil spirits. I do not tolerate blasphemy and those who use knowledge for personal gain.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"8n8NWw9nwPeYQzTr","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"Prayer keeps my mind steadfast and my words are an inspiration to \nthose who have faith. I do not tolerate the concepts of faith and \ndevotion being questioned.","notes":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Prayer keeps my mind steadfast and my words are an inspiration to those who have faith. I do not tolerate the concepts of faith and devotion being questioned.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"j05K9VnQRF3KL1DD","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"My greatest secret is that I am like those I fight. My true essence is that \nof a Yokai ghost, which is why I have a talent for unearthing Broken \nTales. I try to do good deeds in the hope of reincarnating as a human.","notes":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My greatest secret is that I am like those I fight. My true essence is that of a Yokai ghost, which is why I have a talent for unearthing Broken Tales. I try to do good deeds in the hope of reincarnating as a human.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"cTcEilEGGIqU3pzI","name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"Outcome with an Increment: The goal has been reached, and the team has \nbrought home something important. The Storyteller will tell you what.","notes":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Outcome with an Increment: The goal has been reached, and the team has brought home something important. The Storyteller will tell you what.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"0lhBh2tcpy3HVdN3","name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"We are experienced mercenaries and have seen every battlefield. We \nhate working for free and any chance to bring home some extra loot is \ngood.","notes":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are experienced mercenaries and have seen every battlefield. We hate working for free and any chance to bring home some extra loot is good.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KukKSYhCYVYSghA4","name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"We are adept at getting things, information, people, or anything you \nwant - ask and we will find it. We are intolerant of authority and \nanything with a hierarchy of command.","notes":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are adept at getting things, information, people, or anything you want - ask and we will find it. We are intolerant of authority and anything with a hierarchy of command.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vSvABLp7aEADeaLN","name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"Discipline and order are the keys to victory. We act as a team because \nthat is what has allowed us to survive so far. Team first and foremost.","notes":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Discipline and order are the keys to victory. We act as a team because that is what has allowed us to survive so far. Team first and foremost.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"oUu8Z31UUwKIBAsx","name":"Circe the Alchemist - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Circe the Alchemist - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"Eurylochus cannot use more than one Pharmaka special effect per Scene.","notes":"Circe the Alchemist - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Eurylochus cannot use more than one Pharmaka special effect per Scene.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"QGC36kJL6CH3posk","name":"Circe the Alchemist - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Circe the Alchemist - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have studied alchemy with the greatest masters, and my potions can produce wondrous effects. I am so drawn to knowledge that I neglect \nmy own safety.","notes":"Circe the Alchemist - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have studied alchemy with the greatest masters, and my potions can produce wondrous effects. I am so drawn to knowledge that I neglect my own safety.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qqQCmONo7uZkHMDa","name":"Circe the Alchemist - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Circe the Alchemist - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"Eurylochus is my faithful servant pig and helps me with every task. He \nhas an almost human intelligence and one look is enough to understand \nus. I love him like a brother.","notes":"Circe the Alchemist - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Eurylochus is my faithful servant pig and helps me with every task. He has an almost human intelligence and one look is enough to understand us. I love him like a brother.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vZSgwAuELcJ2EIsc","name":"Circe the Alchemist - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Circe the Alchemist - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have a special power over people who are hopelessly attracted to my \npresence. I am shy and often break down when I receive too much \nexplicit attention.","notes":"Circe the Alchemist - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have a special power over people who are hopelessly attracted to my presence. I am shy and often break down when I receive too much explicit attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vuRhYqRJSdVimzGD","name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a good planner and carry all kinds of useful equipment for \nmy work. I hate sudden changes of plans.","notes":"Captain William of Nottingham - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a good planner and carry all kinds of useful equipment for my work. I hate sudden changes of plans.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"J8i0M8K1D6mIvZHs","name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a lawman and I am proud of my office. I have good \nleadership skills and know how to get those in charge to carry out \nan order. I like to be praised for my abilities.","notes":"Captain William of Nottingham - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a lawman and I am proud of my office. I have good leadership skills and know how to get those in charge to carry out an order. I like to be praised for my abilities.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"7UAmsQdbdH9m026n","name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"Years of working as a bounty hunter have made me adept at \nhunting down and eliminating villains. When I am one step away \nfrom my goal, I do not consider retreating.","notes":"Captain William of Nottingham - bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"Years of working as a bounty hunter have made me adept at hunting down and eliminating villains. When I am one step away from my goal, I do not consider retreating.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Dw5NgGlLy6yI32U6","name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am an experienced criminal and I know what it takes to pull off \na perfect heist. Planning and precision are the basis for success, \nand I refuse to rely on improvisation or luck.","notes":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am an experienced criminal and I know what it takes to pull off a perfect heist. Planning and precision are the basis for success, and I refuse to rely on improvisation or luck.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"BemKUgRjWnrwW1mD","name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"My misdeeds have made me a real celebrity - I have clashed with \nheroes, nobles, and religious people, and I know how to deal with \neach of them. Sometimes I like to give my enemies a small \nadvantage just to make the challenge more interesting.","notes":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"My misdeeds have made me a real celebrity - I have clashed with heroes, nobles, and religious people, and I know how to deal with each of them. Sometimes I like to give my enemies a small advantage just to make the challenge more interesting.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241673,"modifiedTime":1783973241673,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vOOMoXYDLkZmiKmS","name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am as ingenious in the use of concealed weapons and low blows \nas I am in plotting crime. The memory of my lost love has changed \nme deeply, and I try to prevent crime from creating innocent \nvictims.","notes":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am as ingenious in the use of concealed weapons and low blows as I am in plotting crime. The memory of my lost love has changed me deeply, and I try to prevent crime from creating innocent victims.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"dx0UW9UlqZQq62hf","name":"The Pale Medic - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Pale Medic - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a good doctor and I know the cure for every disease, I can tell the \nphysical state of health of a patient just by looking at them. I hate \nviolence and physical confrontation.","notes":"The Pale Medic - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a good doctor and I know the cure for every disease, I can tell the physical state of health of a patient just by looking at them. I hate violence and physical confrontation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"QV58622CLVYwfKk1","name":"The Pale Medic - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Pale Medic - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have a certain amount of charm and I know how to put people at ease \nwith my polite manner. I feel uncomfortable in places where I have not \nbeen invited or where it is obvious that my presence is unwelcome.","notes":"The Pale Medic - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have a certain amount of charm and I know how to put people at ease with my polite manner. I feel uncomfortable in places where I have not been invited or where it is obvious that my presence is unwelcome.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"OMeGLPm66slM9o3W","name":"The Pale Medic - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Pale Medic - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have vampire blood in me and my strength is far superior to that of \nan ordinary human. I am extremely sensitive to sunlight and try to \navoid it as much as possible.","notes":"The Pale Medic - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have vampire blood in me and my strength is far superior to that of an ordinary human. I am extremely sensitive to sunlight and try to avoid it as much as possible.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"tNeBWGDGtg1Zs181","name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token.","notes":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"0gQ2zyAO7nQeedlw","name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"We are a harmless middle-aged couple and no one would ever consider \nus a danger. We are adept at going unnoticed. Our passion for human \nfood drives us to real binges.","notes":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"We are a harmless middle-aged couple and no one would ever consider us a danger. We are adept at going unnoticed. Our passion for human food drives us to real binges.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"JkiIL4I9BMBxmkDk","name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"We are always connected to the Mars Operations Center, and this \nallows us to have information about history and science. We are \nmorbidly attracted to any form of art because it is totally absent on our \nworld.","notes":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"We are always connected to the Mars Operations Center, and this allows us to have information about history and science. We are morbidly attracted to any form of art because it is totally absent on our world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"jEHJNCUosyXRfDB9","name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"Our knowledge is far more advanced than human knowledge, and we \nhave incredible technology at our disposal. We always try to help those \nwho are considered outcasts or excluded from society...","notes":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"Our knowledge is far more advanced than human knowledge, and we have incredible technology at our disposal. We always try to help those who are considered outcasts or excluded from society...","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"rRUJMAD2jT2vje7F","name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"Gift - Reanimated Corpse: The Creature is immune to electricity and \ncold. Once per Scene, when an ally is about to take 1 Wound, they can \nactivate this Gift to have the Creature intervene in their defense and take \nthe Wound instead. If Victor is the one requesting the use of this Gift, roll \na die: if it comes up even, the Creature will act to save him by applying the \neffect; if it comes up odd, its deep resentment towards its creator will get \nthe better of it and the Creature will not intervene, skipping its possible \nactivation in the Exchange.","notes":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"Gift - Reanimated Corpse: The Creature is immune to electricity and cold. Once per Scene, when an ally is about to take 1 Wound, they can activate this Gift to have the Creature intervene in their defense and take the Wound instead. If Victor is the one requesting the use of this Gift, roll a die: if it comes up even, the Creature will act to save him by applying the effect; if it comes up odd, its deep resentment towards its creator will get the better of it and the Creature will not intervene, skipping its possible activation in the Exchange.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qp7xznNO99bQZ7aS","name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a luminary in physics and medicine and know secrets that the \nbrightest academics can only dream of. I often get lost in my own \nreasoning, which I articulate aloud without realizing it.","notes":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a luminary in physics and medicine and know secrets that the brightest academics can only dream of. I often get lost in my own reasoning, which I articulate aloud without realizing it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"mHnb3EsZpMC3tqg7","name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I always bring the Creature with me and know how to make the \nmost of its potential. There are times when the guilt of creating such \na monster brings me back to reality, and in those rare moments, I \ntry to do a good deed to atone for my sins.","notes":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I always bring the Creature with me and know how to make the most of its potential. There are times when the guilt of creating such a monster brings me back to reality, and in those rare moments, I try to do a good deed to atone for my sins.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"IIx2hHfcTg4KrUaV","name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"My mad experiments have expanded my knowledge of death and \nthe occult. I can tell the difference between science and magic. I \ngreedily desire anything I deem useful for my research and have no \nqualms about obtaining it.","notes":"Doctor V. Frankenstein - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"My mad experiments have expanded my knowledge of death and the occult. I can tell the difference between science and magic. I greedily desire anything I deem useful for my research and have no qualms about obtaining it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"sWrm47DTbKr9t6Yx","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"If your Champion is knocked out or killed, a new Champion will arrive at \nthe beginning of the next Scenario. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all \nChecks where your action removes you from your Champion’s obsessive \nattention.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"If your Champion is knocked out or killed, a new Champion will arrive at the beginning of the next Scenario. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all Checks where your action removes you from your Champion’s obsessive attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZbIOiRcpSOMelNeX","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have a talent for assessing people’s merits and flaws, so I am good at \ncoordinating the efforts of those who trust me. I have a soft spot for those \nwho fail but try hard, and though I don’t like to admit it, sometimes the \ninstinct to help losers still takes over.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I have a talent for assessing people’s merits and flaws, so I am good at coordinating the efforts of those who trust me. I have a soft spot for those who fail but try hard, and though I don’t like to admit it, sometimes the instinct to help losers still takes over.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9vyxzILtIDis1mgv","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am very vain and love to waste time admiring my own image.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am very vain and love to waste time admiring my own image.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"y1p4waDd0p4lKUom","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am an ancient fairy and my magic allows me to manipulate and \ndominate water. I don’t like to be recognized by humans, so I try to \nkeep my powers hidden from prying eyes.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am an ancient fairy and my magic allows me to manipulate and dominate water. I don’t like to be recognized by humans, so I try to keep my powers hidden from prying eyes.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Vx6F5qoBL2JSKLZO","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"Porziella, my faithful flea, is always with me and has guarded my \nback like a trusted servant. Over time, I have trained Porziella to \nperform various tasks, including very complex ones. Porziella loves \nhuman blood, and although this disgusts people, I try to satisfy her \nwhenever I can.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Porziella, my faithful flea, is always with me and has guarded my back like a trusted servant. Over time, I have trained Porziella to perform various tasks, including very complex ones. Porziella loves human blood, and although this disgusts people, I try to satisfy her whenever I can.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"2goIdSpKvjLgN65W","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I learned some magic tricks from seven bandits, all of them brothers, \nand I know about arcane arts. I am attracted to magic and want to \ngather all knowledge about it.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I learned some magic tricks from seven bandits, all of them brothers, and I know about arcane arts. I am attracted to magic and want to gather all knowledge about it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ibxRnRinPSwq779i","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am courageous and stubborn. When I speak about justice and \nequality, the passion that animates me touches people’s hearts. For me, \nthe cause comes before everything and I am ready to take any action, \neven the most extreme.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am courageous and stubborn. When I speak about justice and equality, the passion that animates me touches people’s hearts. For me, the cause comes before everything and I am ready to take any action, even the most extreme.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241674,"modifiedTime":1783973241674,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"glursGL9MPYrFWSS","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can \nspend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects:\n1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast \nand allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible \nobstacle.\n2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or \ndetails of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift.\n3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action \nthat is not intended to harm anyone. \n4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can spend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects: 1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast and allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible obstacle. 2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or details of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift. 3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action that is not intended to harm anyone. 4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"cejnUpvgTUmzUnXX","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have an unusual mind and remember every detail, even years \nlater. My body is puny and I hate to do strenuous work.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I have an unusual mind and remember every detail, even years later. My body is puny and I hate to do strenuous work.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"BzLPL9pg3nkQ5p7D","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have charisma to spare and I am a smooth talker who commands \nrespect and admiration. I must always have the last word.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I have charisma to spare and I am a smooth talker who commands respect and admiration. I must always have the last word.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AFYnEiY0ZzHCoxsF","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Dark Ego Descriptor"}}}},"system":{"description":"It only takes me a few seconds to assess the situation and use it to \nmy advantage. I have a soft spot for loving families who remind me \nof what I will never have.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"It only takes me a few seconds to assess the situation and use it to my advantage. I have a soft spot for loving families who remind me of what I will never have.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"r1KYb94LQRUAJg7x","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled Hunter and know what it takes to survive in wild \nplaces. I find it hard to trust anyone, but when I do, I never question \nthe good faith of the person I have chosen.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am a skilled Hunter and know what it takes to survive in wild places. I find it hard to trust anyone, but when I do, I never question the good faith of the person I have chosen.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qpevRjXgDBldPqKl","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"My senses are keen and my body is hardened by the outdoors. I hate \nbig cities, hustle and bustle, and generally can’t stand people who talk \ntoo much.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"My senses are keen and my body is hardened by the outdoors. I hate big cities, hustle and bustle, and generally can’t stand people who talk too much.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Xd4gSUrHuTHvjDHB","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am trained to kill all kinds of beasts and know how to use the \nhunting grounds to my advantage. Monsters must always be \ndestroyed, for them I see no mercy or redemption.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am trained to kill all kinds of beasts and know how to use the hunting grounds to my advantage. Monsters must always be destroyed, for them I see no mercy or redemption.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"cqd0Rns8muTWxaOI","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Descriptor 1"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have extremely keen eyesight and no detail escapes me. I can see \neverything, even in the dark or in the thickest fog. Sometimes I don’t \nunderstand whether the things I see are real or just a figment of my \nimagination.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have extremely keen eyesight and no detail escapes me. I can see everything, even in the dark or in the thickest fog. Sometimes I don’t understand whether the things I see are real or just a figment of my imagination.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MAv7cRRtyZpHgUJ4","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Descriptor 2"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am used to walking around completely naked, so my physique is \ntough. I hate having unnecessary things on me, except for my beloved \ncrown.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am used to walking around completely naked, so my physique is tough. I hate having unnecessary things on me, except for my beloved crown.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qTgApPzUHE8g8vRp","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Descriptor 3"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am good with words, I know etiquette, and I know how to dazzle the \ncrowd. I cannot refrain from commenting with the utmost sincerity \non the way my interlocutors dress.","notes":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am good with words, I know etiquette, and I know how to dazzle the crowd. I cannot refrain from commenting with the utmost sincerity on the way my interlocutors dress.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241675,"modifiedTime":1783973241675,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
